@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.19 * tmp + 0.01) / v1))
    tmp = ((0.96 * 0.08) * wp.abs(tmp))
    v2 = ((0.23 / wp.exp(v0 + 0.19)) / ((tmp + 0.19 / v1 + 0.44) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.72)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.60 / v2 + 0.03)) - wp.sin((v2 + 0.60 - v0 + 0.58)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v1 - wp.exp(tmp + 0.87)))
    v1 = (0.85 + 0.99)
    v0 = ((v1 - wp.exp(tmp + 0.44)) - v2)
    v1 = 0.51
    data[tid] = v0
